e...and a lot better i think than the "real" story. that could have and should have worked. instead it became a "creatures living at the end of the old tunnel and everyone knows about it but you, and unless you read the book, well...you just won't ever understand it" fiasco. tragic, what an awful thing to do to a movie with such potential. if you like mindless fake blood and gore, you'll love this. but if you have half a brain in your head then you will completely hate it. stay away- far, far away.

