ee this movie. i applaud stephen king for actually agreeing to sign a contract to not dis stanley kubrik any more. i would never have done that, i would have taken all the rights i could get to yell at him all day. i can't wait to see the 6 hour version, at least it has the hedge animals.rating: 2/10

